44
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:25,600
I don't know.

45
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:28,600
Maybe I'll run against him.

46
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:32,600
Well, you've got my vote.

47
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:37,600
I'm serious, Philip.

48
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:39,600
Why shouldn't I run?

49
