93
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,600
Of course.

94
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:34,600
Why will the voters vote for you against Boswell,

95
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,600
Mrs. Stewart? Stewart

