293
00:19:48,600 --> 00:19:51,600
Maybe we'll all care now.

294
00:19:51,600 --> 00:19:52,600
Good-bye.

295
00:19:52,600 --> 00:19:56,600
Thank you,

296
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:58,600
